PN,38901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FFour rowers crossing the English
OL,8,FChannel in a world-first charity
OL,9,Fchallenge came just "ten feet" from
OL,10,Fpotential disaster, as they narrowly
OL,11,Favoided a large tanker.
OL,13,FThe South-North Adventure team had
OL,14,Fbeen experiencing a series of
OL,15,Ftechnical difficulties with their
OL,16,Fboat, leaving them virtually helpless
OL,17,Fat sea as they drifted into a busy
OL,18,Fshipping lane, 20 miles off the coast
OL,19,Fof Portsmouth.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FThey contacted the Solent Coastguard,
OL,8,Fwho asked a nearby tanker to assist
OL,9,Fbut it got dangerously close after
OL,10,Fthrowing a line for rescue which fell
OL,11,Fshort.
OL,13,FCrew member Kevin Dutton says it was a
OL,14,F"terrifying experience".
OL,16,FHe adds: "It was really, really scary.
OL,17,FThese tankers are huge, they're like
OL,18,Fblocks of terraced houses, even taller.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,F"It passed within about ten feet of
OL,8,Four little ocean rowing boat, and when
OL,9,Fyou're up against a massive tanker
OL,10,Flike that while drifting in a busy
OL,11,Fshipping area, in the middle of the
OL,12,FChannel, it's not exactly a laughing
OL,13,Fmatter."
OL,15,FCrewmate Patrick Neale says they did
OL,16,Fnot have much time to react,
OL,17,Fexplaining: "It was the closest I've
OL,18,Fever been, or ever want to get, to my
OL,19,Ftime being up.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,F"You only had seconds to think about
OL,8,Fit, and I do mean seconds."
OL,10,FShortly after their narrow escape, the
OL,11,Fcrew managed to re-establish contact
OL,12,Fwith the Coastguard and a Border Force
OL,13,Fpatrol vessel came to their rescue,
OL,14,Ftaking them on board and towing their
OL,15,Fboat to Weymouth.
OL,17,FKevin says: "They were absolute
OL,18,Fprofessionals. An incredible team
OL,19,Fturning what was an imminent disaster
OL,20,Fand near-death experience, into a
OL,21,Fseamless rescue."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FThe group are attempting to row, walk
OL,8,Fand cycle from Les Minquiers off the
OL,9,Fcoast of Jersey to the Shetland island
OL,10,Fof Out Stack, in an expedition across
OL,11,Fwhat they call the "real" south-to-
OL,12,Fnorth of the British Isles.
OL,14,FThey are raising money for mental
OL,15,Fhealth charities including Every Child
OL,16,FOur Future and the Big Kid Foundation,
OL,17,Fwith celebrities including snooker
OL,18,Fstars Ronnie O'Sullivan and Jimmy
OL,19,FWhite and This Morning's Ben Shephard
OL,20,Fplanning to join them at various
OL,21,Fpoints of their challenge.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FThe team started their row across the
OL,8,FEnglish Channel from Jersey on
OL,9,FThursday (16 April), after linking up
OL,10,Fwith Iron Maiden singer Bruce
OL,11,FDickinson during their cycle through
OL,12,Fthe island.
OL,14,FThe team's departure had already been
OL,15,Frepeatedly delayed by bad weather, and
OL,16,Fby Friday evening they had run into
OL,17,Ffurther trouble, after a series of
OL,18,Fincreasingly serious problems with
OL,19,Ftheir vessel.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FThe boat's bow line snagged on the
OL,8,Fmooring, meaning they were forced to
OL,9,Fcut themselves free.
OL,11,FConditions continued to hamper
OL,12,Fprogress, causing communication
OL,13,Fissues, a rudder malfunction, and
OL,14,Fthree separate autopilot systems
OL,15,Ffailing - which resulted in the boat
OL,16,Fdrifting without power or control.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FThe other two crew members, Billy
OL,8,FTaylor and Gary Hutchings, are highly
OL,9,Fexperienced ocean rowers, who say they
OL,10,Fhad "never known so many things go
OL,11,Fwrong on a boat, one thing after
OL,12,Fanother failed".
OL,14,FDespite all of these issues, the group
OL,15,Fremain undeterred from completing
OL,16,Ftheir race from the southernmost to
OL,17,Fthe northernmost points of the British
OL,18,FIsles.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777050358
OL,3,CRowers 'ten feet' from tanker
OL,4,Ccollision after drifting into shipping
OL,5,Clane
OL,7,FKevin adds: "Well you know what they
OL,8,Fsay, when you fall off the horse you
OL,9,Fjust get straight back on.
OL,11,F"We're cracking straight on with the
OL,12,Fcycling leg now and we're going to go
OL,13,Fback and continue from where we were
OL,14,Frescued.
OL,16,F"I have to say the support so far has
OL,17,Fbeen amazing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
